# Cyber Assessment Framework


This report was generated after completing a self-assessment of the Cyber Assessment Framework from the National Cyber Security Centre within Cortex XSOAR.

A review of the Cyber Assessment Framework can be found [here](https://www.ncsc.gov.uk/collection/caf)
# CAF Objective A - Managing security risk
# CAF Objective B - Protecting against cyber-attack
# CAF Objective C - Detecting cyber security events
# CAF Objective D - Minimising the impact of cyber security incidents

# NCSC CAF Assessment Details

For each objective, the quesitons below show whether your response was 'Achieved', 'Not Achieved' or 'Partially Achieved'.
